 G0_Overview {
  m_sTitle "Overview"
  m_sTextData "American <b>tank and mechanized infantry company team</b> counter attacks along a railway line seized by the NVA."\
  ""\
  "At least 3 Bradleys must be slotted"
  m_bEmptyFactionVisibility 1
 }
 U1_Situation {
  coords 0 0 0
  m_sTitle "I. SITUATION"
  m_sTextData "<b>a. Enemy Forces</b>"\
  ""\
  "One day ago, an NVA motorized rifle battalion attacked southwards along road and railway line, likely as part of an ongoing effort to secure important supply routes that could eventually support a larger scale advance through the region."\
  ""\
  "The enemies forwardmost company is located around Koskelankyla / Pauhu, likely waiting for follow on forces to continue the advance."\
  ""\
  "The enemy battalion is using BTR-70 infantry fighting vehicles supported by T-72A tanks. They may be able to request air support, likely in the form of an attack helicopter, however not in significant numbers."\
  ""\
  ""\
  "<b>b. Friendly Forces</b>"\
  ""\
  "2 tank platoons (Abrams) and 1 mechanized infantry platoon (BFV), part of a <b>tank and mechanized infantry company team</b>."\
  ""\
  "There are additional forces preparing to follow and support the counter attack, fully securing bypassed enemy positions."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "US"
  }
  m_iOrder 1
 }
 U2_Mission {
  coords 0 0 0
  m_sTitle "II. MISSION"
  m_sTextData "The tank and mechanized infantry company team counter-attacks the NVA battalion situated within a kilometer of the railway line, enabling friendly follow and support forces to secure bypassed enemy positions."\
  ""\
  "It should penetrate its defenses by assaulting some and bypassing other enemy positions."\
  ""\
  "The following settlements must be assaulted:"\
  "- Pauhu"\
  "- Either Koskelankyla OR Virpimaki"\
  "- Either Ruha, Muilunkyla and Ruhanpera, OR Latvamuilu, Letho and Valimaki"\
  ""\
  "A settlement counts as assaulted if a Bradley was within it for 1 minute, it does not actually have to be fully cleared. When Bradleys approach a settlement, some friendly infantry is spawned."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "US"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
 U3_Execution {
  coords 0 0 0
  m_sTitle "III. EXECUTION"
  m_sTextData "<b>a. Commander's Intent</b>"\
  ""\
  "The intent of this operation is to regain control over the area, spoiling immediate attacks further along the railway line."\
  ""\
  "To achieve this, the tank and mechanized infantry company team will assault several enemy positions, penetrating the enemies defense and creating gaps that can be exploited by follow and support forces tasked with fully securing bypassed positions."\
  ""\
  "The following settlements must be assaulted:"\
  "- Pauhu"\
  "- Either Koskelankyla OR Virpimaki"\
  "- Either Ruha, Muilunkyla and Ruhanpera, OR Latvamuilu, Letho and Valimaki"\
  ""\
  "<b>b. Concept of the operation</b>"\
  ""\
  "The chosen objectives should be assaulted approximately in a mostly linear order."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "US"
  }
  m_iOrder 3
 }
